    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Notitia de terra de Piscina Lifredi et da Sancto Fridiano et de Pratale. In
                        Christi nomine. Breve pro futuris et modernis temporibus securitatem ac
                        firmitatem ad memoriam habendam vel retinendam, qualiter infra civitate
                            <placeName ref="#places/66"
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Mention #Residential #Palatium #Emperor/king"
                            >Pisa</placeName>, in <rs key="#Palatium #Emperor/king">palatio domni
                            regis</rs>, in placido residisse domina <persName key="#Marquis/duke"
                            ref="#people/292">Beatrix</persName>
                        <rs key="#Marquis/duke">ducatrix et marchionissa</rs> hac causas audienda
                        hac deliberanda, residentibus cum ea, <persName key="#Witness #Judge"><name
                                ref="Hubertus">Uberto</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Judge"><name ref="Winizo">Winitho</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness #Judge"><name ref="Heinricus"
                            >Enrigo</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness #Judge"><name
                                ref="Hugo">Ugo</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness #Judge"
                                ><name ref="Signorectus">Signorecto</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Judge"><name ref="Lambertus">Lamberto</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness #Judge"><name ref="Ildebrandus"
                                >Ildebrando</name></persName> et alio <persName
                            key="#Witness #Judge"><name ref="Hugo">Ugo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudicibus</rs>, <persName key="#Witness #Causidicus"><name
                                ref="Hugo">Ugo</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Causidicus"><name ref="Sisemundus"
                            >Sesmundo</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness #Causidicus"><name
                                ref="Winizo">Winizo</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Causidicus">Bernardo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Causidicus">causidicis</rs>, <persName key="#Witness #Notary"
                                ><name ref="Wido">Wido</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Notary"><name ref="Cuneradus">Currado</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notariis</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Sicherius">Sicheri</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Mattus">Matti</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Lambertus">Lamberto</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Speciosus">Speciosi</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Rodelandus">Rodilando</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Rodelandus">Rollandi</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Contulinus"
                            >Gontulino</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Pandulfus"
                                >Pandolfi</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Rodulfinus">Rodolfino</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Rodelandus">Rollandi</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Eritius">Erizo</name></persName> filio
                                <persName><name ref="Heinricus">Enrigi</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Iohannes">Iohanni</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Wido">Widi</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Baroncellus">Baroncello</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Ermengarda">Hermigarde</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Gandulfus"
                            >Glandolfo</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Carolus"
                                >Carli</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Alcherius">Alcheri</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Ildebrandus">Ildibrandi</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Leo">Leo</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Rusticus">Rustici</name></persName>, et
                        reliquis pluribus. Ibique eorum presentiis venientes <persName key="#Priors"
                            ref="#people/256">Bonitho</persName>
                        <rs key="#Priors">prior</rs> de <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/78" key="#Monasteries">Domini et Sancti
                            Quirici et Sancti Salvatori et Sancte Marie et Sancti
                            Benedicti</orgName> de <placeName ref="#places/86" key="#Monasteries"
                            >Populonio</placeName> proclamavit una cum <persName key="#Advocatus"
                                ><name ref="Hugo">Ugo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Advocatus">avocato</rs> suprascripti monasterii quod
                                <persName><name ref="Peregrinus de Vignale"
                            >Peregrino</name></persName> de <placeName ref="#places/132"
                            >Vignale</placeName> filius bone menorie *** contendit suprascripto
                        monasterii tres <rs key="#Petiae">petiis</rs> de terris, quibus sunt positi
                        in loco et finibus <placeName ref="#places/91" key="#Petiae"
                            >Cornino</placeName>, una ubi dicitur <placeName ref="#places/130"
                            key="#Petiae">Piscina Lifredi</placeName>, secunda ubi dicitur
                            <placeName ref="#places/131" key="#Petiae">Sancto Fridiano</placeName>,
                        tertia ubi dicitur <placeName ref="#places/131" key="#Petiae"
                            >Pratale</placeName>, de quibus suprascripto prior una cum <persName
                            key="#Abbots" ref="#people/108">Cunizo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbate</rs> suo et de suprascripto monasterio, <rs
                            key="#Judicial_breve">proclamaverunt</rs> domine <persName
                            ref="#people/125">Mattilde</persName>. Cum suprascripta domina Beatrix
                        proclamationem audisse, per fustes quas in suis detinebat manibus,
                        investivit cum consilio iudicum suprascripto priore una cum suprascripto
                        avocato suo, pro suprascripto monasterio de suprascriptis tres petiis de
                        terris et insuper misit <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king #Marquis/duke #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium"
                            >bannum</rs> domni regis super predicto priore et super iam dicto
                        avocato suo et super predicto monasterio in bisantios aureos duomilia, ut
                        nullus quilibet homo, magna parvaque persona, eodem monasterio de predictis
                        rebus sine legale iudicio disvestire presumat. Qui vero fecerit, predicti
                        duomilia bisanteos aureos composituro se agnoscat, medietatem <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king #Camera_regis">regali camere</rs> et alia
                        medie|[tatem] suprascripti monasterii eiusque rectoribus. Hoc factum est
                        anno dominice incarnationis millesimo septuagesimo VI, idibus martii,
                        indictione quarta Xa. Quidem et ego <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name
                                ref="Arimundus">Erimundus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> domni inperatoris ex iussione suprascripte
                        domine Beatrix seo iudicum ammonitjone scripsi. Winizo regis iudex interfui
                        et subscripsi. Henricus iudex sacri palatii interfui et subscripsi.
                        Lambertus iudex sacri palatii interfui et subscripsi. Ugo iudex sacri
                        palatii interfui et subscripsi. <persName key="#Witness #Judge"><name
                                ref="Teudericus">Teodericus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> sacri palatii interfui et subscripsi. Ugo
                        causidicus ibi fui et subscripsi. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
